  ~o~  Vampire Blood Energy  ~o~
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Blood is the source of all energy to function as a Vampire.  Fresh blood can
only be gotten from the corpses of vanquished victims and without it, you will
lose the ability to use any of your commands or spells.

  Your blood level energy is located at the bottom of your score and has the
following values:  CRITICAL, ANEMIC, LOW, MEDIUM, HIGH, ROBUST.
